            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae Nemesi <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Diogenes <lb n="3"/>et Silia Valeria <lb n="4"/>pro salute sua et <lb n="5"/>filiorum suorum <lb n="6"/>mater et pater <lb n="7"/>ex voto a solo <lb n="8"/>templum ex suo <lb n="9"/>fecerunt colle<lb break="no" n="10"/>gio utric<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>lari</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="11"/>orum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 10: überliefert ist VIRI CLARI. (B): Alicu: Z. 10/11: u[t]riclari/orum.</p>
            </div>
